Package ca.uhn.fhir.jpa.term.api

Interface ITermDeferredStorageSvc

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TermDeferredStorageSvcImpl
    public interface ITermDeferredStorageSvc
    This service handles processing "deferred" concept writes, meaning concepts that have neen queued for storage because there are too many of them to handle in a single transaction.
